The Alex Jones Show
Friday, 20 September 2013


[sebaygo1]


Show Description
................
From the Infowars web site :: On this Friday, September 20 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex covers a wide range of compelling topics with a full roster of dynamic guests. 

Rocky Anderson, the former mayor of Salt Lake City, Utah, joins the show to talk about his disgust towards the NSA for spying on communications during the 2002 Winter Olympic games, calling it "the greatest scandal of the century." 

Alex welcomes American economist Dr. Paul Craig Roberts to the broadcast to examine the accelerating implosion of the U.S. economy. 

The Health Ranger, Mike Adams also joins the transmission to discuss psychotropic drugs and the role they play in violent crimes.
